{"tid":1379941,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"當天我驅散憔悴 今天我歸去如水","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:06.000Z","uid":276834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ede082e360ba7210fed44e9631a13dd54cb6f8e4","tid":1379941,"uid":276834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"《柔韌如水》（改自:滿地可 何韻詩）<br />\n<br />\n元朗 鐵路染色<br />\n無法接受這 警察<br />\n竟會 比惡勢力更可怕<br />\n誰叫 這是我家<br />\n誰叫 垃圾政府偷偷侵佔我的<br />\n應有自由本色<br />\n<br />\n當天我驅散憔悴<br />\n今天我歸去如水<br />\n就算子彈翻飛霧裡豁出去<br />\n未擊退 匯湧於街區<br />\n白色恐襲裡 敢說能言永不衰<br />\n<br />\n離去 退路已阻<br />\n前去 棍落棒打<br />\n官方掩耳惹民憤 一起舉傘反擊<br />\n<br />\n當天我驅散憔悴<br />\n今天我歸去如水<br />\n就算子彈翻飛霧裡豁出去<br />\n未擊退 匯湧於街區<br />\n人海以愛點起曙光 誓護衞我香港<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing<br />\nSinging the song of our home<br />\n就算跌跌碰碰 活了這些年<br />\n在這裡 我都不心虛 曾經愛過的 都有追<br />\n蠻力尚未有累<br />\n<br />\n當天我驅散憔悴<br />\n今天我歸去如水<br />\n讓我痛痛快快 活了這些年<br />\n又歸去 記憶的街區<br />\n仍不愧面對<br />\n小店仍存這小島裡<br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n之前放錯台沉底，希望有人可以幫忙執執佢同唱🙇🏻🙇🏻<br />\n<br />\n小妹第一次改詞，好似有啲唔順，請幫手執執&amp;唱🙇🏻🙇🏻"},{"pid":"d8f8c70c516fdf54ebc0dd5a05fa86802519ce1a","tid":1379941,"uid":38237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:41:38.000Z","msg":"--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打爆啲交通燈會唔會易過全民死火燈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------"},{"pid":"849974bb4f2be586d41bac889222e37f37252bd7","tid":1379941,"uid":269647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家花一分鐘睇一睇<br />\n唔該崇洋嘅入一入嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379814</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-"},{"pid":"eba338e98d11d592442b577ca1021ef2dbea357e","tid":1379941,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing 想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0c90607d80943da61a8827f150c75619e50c07","tid":1379941,"uid":276834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba338e98d11d592442b577ca1021ef2dbea357e","tid":1379941,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing 想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"因為已經諗唔到等比人改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}